{"tid":1066391,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再覆游學修最新回應","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:43:23.000Z","uid":126168,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d039766e7f9a2fa1a2af9ebde2cd23e3fe48563","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事源曾樂彤咪嘴事件<br />\n證明呢2個人冇品又冇家教</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最近出左份偽道歉</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKnFvBi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKnFvBi.png&h=8a8b2f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好再覆佢 唔好再鬧佢<br />\n尤其人身攻擊<br />\n（唔要豬隊友）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">而家佢地就係想轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想比人覺得我已經道歉左<br />\n但仲要俾咁多人繼續批評<br />\n我好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想得到人哋憐憫<br />\n然後我哋就當正哂壞人角色<br />\n佢一直而家就係證明緊俾人睇d hater存在<br />\n（存乜撚野在 係你地自己做錯 講事實咋）<br />\n局外人係會覺得佢係真心道歉<br />\n之後自此就會這呢件事講到自己有幾抑鬱<br />\n好堅強 黎博好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歪理當真理<br />\n事實同理據都係我地度<br />\n所以係其他報導都得到好多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（因為好多人冇連登ac留唔到</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔好俾人哋覺得我哋好唔理智<br />\n所以佢篇文 唔該唔好再回覆<br />\n尤其嗰啲人身攻擊</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再比呢啲冇家教嘅人奸計得逞</span></ins>"},{"pid":"1ebfbe9dd2e07e22725354543044b1e21724e85e","tid":1066391,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thispersondoesnotexist.com/image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthispersondoesnotexist.com%2Fimage&h=7004e289&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9c89c286fe0cc063090cc256a38d800e7f531f0","tid":1066391,"uid":57520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"566eab79098f10ffeecddff75cdb2e80b514cb09","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b07716498917cd8a4e1df51d261132f4dc072ca","tid":1066391,"uid":141330,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:13:40.000Z","msg":"樓主係游學修本人？"},{"pid":"6b5907cbb1bb19a074275819034a27b035666549","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:17:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋而家要槍口對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪咀都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係佢態度 觀眾無辜<br />\n講事實都要俾佢問候老母<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個人根本就係同我地鬥緊<br />\n佢依家需要大量人支持<br />\n所以就出左呢招<br />\n大家請勿中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3243012cc048d75f498989f2a285ffff42e68205","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b07716498917cd8a4e1df51d261132f4dc072ca","tid":1066391,"uid":141330,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:13:40.000Z","msg":"樓主係游學修本人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"請細閱我當中的文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b143e053aa21da4b68f08872b4e18dda2adafc99","tid":1066391,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"佢張圖係偷圖"},{"pid":"6cf36f0005b4a6d9c5482055bcacf7c7ad070e28","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"b143e053aa21da4b68f08872b4e18dda2adafc99","tid":1066391,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"佢張圖係偷圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"根本就無心道歉<br />\n句句有骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564cd2d4a742d9f2eca4f0e9239bb6721e2cff0c","tid":1066391,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"俾人屈咪嘴仲要俾你班小學雞係咁踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e27582b6b35137925e6a1cf7b15c89934286391","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"0490a2f52dcb4cf0e40ff22f83010a22d3a2a4da","tid":1066391,"uid":126168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:30:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a691b2bfc4d5d9ec4e3694f33cd031e590e2a70","tid":1066391,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d42dd31b984cd24cf1bf01d3982768750f68afdc","tid":1066391,"uid":30930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"564157f64b8d0b6489a274e167f4b50dcaf9a877","tid":1066391,"uid":66048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2QBK0Dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2QBK0Dc.jpg&h=57c21a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱又出過一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi